---
import Layout from '../../layouts/main.astro';

// Redirect to home if not in development mode
if (!import.meta.env.DEV) {
  return Astro.redirect('/');
}
---

<Layout title="Markdown Test - Development Only">
  <article class="container mx-auto py-12 px-4 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="mb-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Markdown Test Page</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
        Development page - Testing markdown rendering and typography
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-warning-light border border-warning rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-warning">
          ⚠️ This page is available only in development mode
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Markdown Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
      <h2>Heading 2</h2>
      <p>This is a paragraph with <strong>bold text</strong> and <em>italic text</em>. It demonstrates the basic typography of the PIU theme.</p>
      
      <h3>Heading 3</h3>
      <p>Here's a list of features:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Custom PIU color palette</li>
        <li>Dark mode support</li>
        <li>Responsive design</li>
        <li>Modern typography</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Code Examples</h3>
      <p>Here's some inline code: <code>const isDev = import.meta.env.DEV</code></p>
      
      <pre><code>{`// Block code example
function useJupiterPrices() {
  const [prices, setPrices] = useState(null);
  const [isLoading, setIsLoading] = useState(false);
  
  useEffect(() => {
    fetchPrices();
  }, []);
  
  return { prices, isLoading };
}`}</code></pre>

      <h3>Links and References</h3>
      <p>Here's a link to the <a href="https://dev.jup.ag/docs/price-api/v3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jupiter Price API documentation</a>.</p>

      <h3>Blockquote</h3>
      <blockquote>
        <p>"The best way to predict the future is to create it."</p>
        <cite>— Peter Drucker</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <h3>Table Example</h3>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Token</th>
            <th>Price</th>
            <th>Change 24h</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>SOL</td>
            <td>$237.52</td>
            <td>-2.42%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>PIU</td>
            <td>$0.000022</td>
            <td>-2.91%</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3>Horizontal Rule</h3>
      <hr />

      <h3>Images</h3>
      <p>Here's how images would be rendered in markdown:</p>
      <p><em>Note: This is just a placeholder for image rendering</em></p>

      <h2>Conclusion</h2>
      <p>This markdown test page demonstrates how content would be rendered with the PIU theme. The typography should be clean, readable, and consistent with the overall design system.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>